Oikopleura data

Source: R/oikData.R
oikData.Rd

Oikopleura data points to overlay on nucleotide distance / scrambling index plots.

Usage

oikData

Format

List of tibbles. The name of each tibble is just a time stamp.

Details

This test dataset is derived from genome alignments produced by a beta version of the https://nf-co.re/pairgenomealign pipeline.

  • 2025_02_17 6 distances using the RY128 seed.

  • 2025_02_25 10 distances using the RY4 seed.

  • 2025_02_25 10 distances (5 windows per sequence feature) using the MAM8 seed and the 2.1~beta pipeline.

See also

Other Lazy-loaded data: Haloarchaea

Author

Charles Plessy

oikData
